# ai-workspace root is local-only — never commit it as an umbrella repo.
# This .gitignore is defense-in-depth: deny everything, then whitelist only the
# workspace meta files and the .claude/ tooling below.

*

!.gitignore
!README.md
!CLAUDE.md
!CLAUDE.template.md
!CONTEXT.template.md
!HANDBOOK.md
!PROJECTS.md
!.claude/
!.claude/**

# Generated, local-only dashboard output. The generator script stays tracked
# (it's whitelisted above via .claude/**); this regenerated HTML is not.
.claude/dashboard/dashboard.html
